      <div class="module-card__top">
        <div class="module-card__icon">📐</div>
        <span class="badge badge--soon">Coming soon</span>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card__code">ANA · Module 4</div>
      <div class="module-card__title">Analytical Mechanics</div>
      <div class="module-card__desc">Lagrangian, Hamiltonian, the principle of least action. The deep structure of classical physics.</div>
      <div class="module-card__meta">
